mas.agentsHempelsSofa.data.zone

Class Zone

  • java.lang.Object
    • mas.agentsHempelsSofa.data.zone.Zone
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Believable

    public class Zone
extends Object
implements Believable
    An implementation of a zone. It provides the following information:
    • the vertices in the zone
    • the critical frontier vertices
    • the agent tokens in the zone
    • the agent tokens on critical frontier vertices
    • a percepted value
    • the stability value
    Author:
    Hempels-Sofa
